'''Tritacale''' was a flavorful [[Vegetable/Legends|vegetable]] grown on [[Dantooine/Legends|Dantooine]]. It could enhance the flavors in any dish.

[[Griggen Sylo|Griggen]] and [[Tashna Sylo]] harvested tritacale to feed their children as well as to sell offworld.

